{"tid":2510073,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿燦廖偉雄復出做 YouTuber","createTime":"2021-04-30T01:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T08:40:53.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"72d90a48a10d8fe722c337f755b1dd4efb8ddcf1","tid":2510073,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:45:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/N_X6wf9wp30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FN_X6wf9wp30&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=90f53e79\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/N_X6wf9wp30</a><br />\n<br />\n百貨應百客？用殘體字？ 🙄"},{"pid":"5cfc7ed0a50b304d7f85eb7dfc4394942c5854a1","tid":2510073,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:46:01.000Z","msg":"63歲廖偉雄於1976年參加無綫藝員訓練班入行，初出道在電視劇《網中人》中飾演大陸新移民「阿燦」而為人熟知，及後又在搞笑電視節目《笑星救地球》中反串「乜太」，成一時經典。他在1990年代後期淡出，專心一致從商，但1999年因為直銷生意而欠債40幾萬港元，被銀行入稟追討申請破產，廖偉雄因而再重返演藝圈一段時間。"},{"pid":"b8575f99b1bf5db1164ce76c381e5bd816eabc07","tid":2510073,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:46:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8puoJYS0vO8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8puoJYS0vO8&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=06f3a759\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8puoJYS0vO8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/32cFnpGN4_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F32cFnpGN4_4&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=e9bfd7d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/32cFnpGN4_4</a><br />\n笑星救地球"},{"pid":"7d43fd81251efa33e99658364f52e26ad074afe2","tid":2510073,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:46:34.000Z","msg":"2001年，廖偉雄再次轉型，於馬來西亞擔任燒味廚師，製作「燦師傅」叉燒；之後定居廣東羅定市，專注發展有機農業，他種植的「亞燦米」仲獲得多項殊榮。<br />\n<br />\n廖偉雄現在沒拍劇，專心打理生意之餘更「復出」開設YouTube頻道，親自做主持去介紹「亞燦米」及「亞燦雞」。在片中他用一貫的幽默作風介紹自己如何養雞，對白及表情都非常「生鬼」。"},{"pid":"517fb8bf1bbdd48f428b853ad9229436d4a5b4a4","tid":2510073,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:46:46.000Z","msg":"去年9月他開設YouTube頻道，有數段影片都是講述他做生意的心得及經歷，名為《亞燦米是這樣走過來的》。表示在初初開賣「亞燦米」時有人用30萬買了香港代理權，「結果只是賣出2公斤」；直言「亞燦米」頭3年都沒有太多生意，一包包大米積滿貨倉，「但我哋無放棄過，因為係我哋嘅理想。」<br />\n<br />\n在2015年，廖偉雄短暫回到娛樂圈舉行「演笑會」，不過當時他曾接受訪問時指自己暫時無意拍劇，「長時間拍劇會好辛苦，而家拍電視劇，體力支撐唔到。返娛樂圈有好多可以做，可以出書或者其他工作。」"},{"pid":"3f020ce0c1315643fb7381ef2866fdd51cd3f1e0","tid":2510073,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T01:47:08.000Z","msg":"之後「亞燦米」獲得多項殊榮，除了成為全國十大好米之一外，更是中國華南地區唯一一個攞到國際3大認證嘅大米。廖偉雄也曾與旅行社合作搞旅行團，帶大家參觀他的「燦神龍場」，加深大眾對有機農業同食品的了解。而除了「亞燦米」外也致力於發展名為「亞燦雞」的養雞場。"},{"pid":"8c7fcdd05a1e5c08f655f445bfe7e214ac9b3ff7","tid":2510073,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:03:33.000Z","msg":"燦神已過氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca2b167af1af1ef5409eb4df97d342e81dbfcd1","tid":2510073,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c7fcdd05a1e5c08f655f445bfe7e214ac9b3ff7","tid":2510073,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:03:33.000Z","msg":"燦神已過氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:51:45.000Z","msg":"而家講返佢d對白都未必有人知講緊邊個 🙄"},{"pid":"d56a3d30bb230094930e3ec4feed81e4d5c4af20","tid":2510073,"uid":211461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"香港公投：你會食邊隻米？<br />\n泰國米 (產地：泰國) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿燦米 (產地：中国) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1113a2bdcdd2562f54d6acd54f7b1f948e12b52f","tid":2510073,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdyfZpi4Lb6PppBD94BnFpWkJLpJ36UqE9uU6TyiKVXxE?filename=LQ5CNLu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQ5CNLu.jpg&h=75ab5afe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"970a19be8a7a6b81d9222f7fbc20076f90c1b036","tid":2510073,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"廢老過期藝人<br />\n將長輩圖既味道帶上youtube"},{"pid":"f9f295edcbadd917c8377a3d860b8b3d1a99c3ef","tid":2510073,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接返cctvb？<br />\n啱晒喎"},{"pid":"d530b90dab06df5c500600117607a1bee0c206a1","tid":2510073,"uid":161731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmemhTy3gHyVPUcRXoeHwbirkW6c11NGz47SKPQaB3ZJx4?filename=Y8p798e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY8p798e.jpg&h=3d8604cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4560dff5597f0e5805293e286086b280cd0a37f1","tid":2510073,"uid":47226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"笑聲救地球真係好好笑，十幾廿年前同張如城做嗰個咩香港鬆一鬆已經回哂塘，而家更加唔駛睇"},{"pid":"e17512bc6d1704aa722210bfb33d03fb5508624a","tid":2510073,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"97前笑大陸喱叫阿燦<br />\n家陣阿燦真係做咗阿燦, 做乜唔講埋蝗語呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw搞生意搞足廿年, 發咗達上咗市未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48716e0d44d8dbecc10df19e972f5576af0ef917","tid":2510073,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e17512bc6d1704aa722210bfb33d03fb5508624a","tid":2510073,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T03:39:13.000Z","msg":"97前笑大陸喱叫阿燦<br />\n家陣阿燦真係做咗阿燦, 做乜唔講埋蝗語呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw搞生意搞足廿年, 發咗達上咗市未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"9